NAME
       ybmtopbm - convert a Bennet Yee 'face' file to PBM


SYNOPSIS
       ybmtopbm

       [facefile]


DESCRIPTION
       This program is part of Netpbm(1).

       ymtopbm reads a file acceptable to the face and xbm pro-
       grams by Bennet Yee (bsy+@cs.cmu.edu).  and writes a PBM
       image as output.

       pbmtoybm(1), pbm(1)
